Actor Luzuko Nteleko featured in several television productions, including Zone 14, Muvhango and Ring of Lies. (Screengrab/eNCA) JOHANNESBURG - The entertainment industry has suffered another loss. Actor Luzuko Nteleko has died. READ: Actress Shaleen Surtie-Richards dies The 36-year-old featured in several television productions, including Zone 14, Muvhango, and Ring of Lies. Tributes have been pouring in on social media from fans and fellow thespians. The cause of death is not yet known.